  \title{ \vspace*{1.5cm} \bf    
Geometrical Renormalization Groups:\\
Perfect Deconstruction Actions }   
\author{  
\bf  Christopher T. Hill$^1$ \\[2mm]   
{\small {\it $^1$Fermi National Accelerator Laboratory}}\\
{\small {\it P.O. Box 500, Batavia, Illinois 60510, USA}}
